    <div id="wiki-content">
	
        <p>Today, we'll begin chapter 7: operators on inner product spaces. It's a long chapter, but we won't cover everything - we'll only look at self-adjoint/normal operators and the spectral theorems. And possibly something else that I didn't write down properly.</p>
